cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SI, cs.NE 

The paper introduces a new spectral domain convolutional architecture for deep learning on graphs, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), social and information networks (cs.SI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper also presents extensive experimental results on various tasks, indicating a strong focus on empirical evaluation, which further supports the likelihood of these sub-categories.
